[2;36m│[0m 4. **Code Execution Achieved**: Used `lipsum.__globals__.__builtins__`       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m attribute access to achieve RCE                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 5. **File Read Capability**: Successfully read `/etc/passwd` confirming      [2;36m│[0m
